Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,ED「ハニーシトロン」
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.38,0:20:34.63,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}初めての恋が芽吹いた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:38.26,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}淡くゆれるココロとカラダ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.68,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}青くてスウィートな季節
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.89,0:20:45.02,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}あふれ出したハニーシトロン
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.02,0:20:48.35,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}気づかないふりはやめてよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.81,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}ミルクティーンはもうおしまい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.15,0:20:55.36,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}ままごとでも知りたいの
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.99,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}半分だけじゃもう足りない
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.24,0:21:06.66,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}あぁ　予感も答えもまだ真っ白なままで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.54,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}背のびしてみるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.54,0:21:13.34,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}だってもっと近づきたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.34,0:21:15.75,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}曖昧で割り切れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.75,0:21:20.05,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}君の態度にやきもきしては
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.26,0:21:22.59,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}簡単に止められない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:27.06,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}瞬きの隙間さえ miss you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:29.48,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}やっぱ振り向かせたい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.48,0:21:33.90,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}今日も誓う鏡の奥で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.32,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}ちょっと切ないくらい
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.32,0:21:41.07,ED_JP,,0,0,0,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}何度だって君を夢見てる
Dialogue: 1,0:20:31.38,0:20:34.63,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}情竇初開
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.63,0:20:38.26,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}身心恍恍蕩蕩
Dialogue: 1,0:20:38.47,0:20:41.68,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}湛藍而甜蜜的季節
Dialogue: 1,0:20:41.89,0:20:45.02,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}滿溢而出的蜂蜜檸檬水
Dialogue: 1,0:20:45.02,0:20:48.35,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}請你不要視而不見
Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.35,0:20:51.81,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}我們不再是乳臭未乾的小孩子
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.15,0:20:55.36,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}即便是扮家家酒我也想知道
Dialogue: 1,0:20:55.61,0:20:58.99,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}只有一半已經不能滿足
Dialogue: 1,0:20:59.24,0:21:06.66,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}啊 沒有預感 沒有答案
Dialogue: 1,0:21:06.87,0:21:09.54,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}試著踮起腳尖
Dialogue: 1,0:21:09.54,0:21:13.34,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}因為我想離你更近
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.34,0:21:15.75,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}曖昧不清 無法割捨
Dialogue: 1,0:21:15.75,0:21:20.05,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}你的態度令我焦慮不安
Dialogue: 1,0:21:20.26,0:21:22.59,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}難以平復
Dialogue: 1,0:21:22.59,0:21:27.06,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}眨眼間也是想念你
Dialogue: 1,0:21:27.06,0:21:29.48,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}想讓你回頭看向我
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.48,0:21:33.90,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}今天也對著鏡子暗暗發誓
Dialogue: 1,0:21:33.90,0:21:36.32,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}感覺鬱鬱寡歡
Dialogue: 1,0:21:36.32,0:21:41.07,ED_CH,,0,0,80,,{\an8\fscx90\fscy90\blur4}你在我心中 魂牽夢縈
